org.intermine.biovalidator.validator.csv

Class CsvColumnMatrics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.biovalidator.validator.csv.CsvColumnMatrics

  • public class CsvColumnMatrics
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents metrics of a columns of a csv file. For each column value it count total number of booleans, integer, floats and patterns.
